<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Nova+Mono&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Material+Symbols+Outlined:opsz,wght,FILL,GRAD@24,400,0,0" />
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Urbanist:ital,wght@0,100..900;1,100..900&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <title>H-api</title>
    <style>
        *{
            box-sizing: content-box;
            margin: 0rem;
            padding: 0rem;
            font-family: "Nova Mono", monospace;
        }
        .heading{
            font-size: 3rem;
            padding: 1rem;
            color: rgb(99, 99, 5);
            text-shadow: .2rem .2rem .2rem yellow;
            background-color: rgb(231, 252, 156);
            border-radius: 0rem 0rem 1.5rem 1.5rem;
        }
        .sub{
            font-size: 1.5rem;
            text-shadow: none;
            padding: 1rem;
            color: black;
        }
        .allLinks{
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns:30% 30% 30%;
            width: fit-content;
            margin: 3rem auto;
            padding: 2rem;
            gap: 4rem;
        }
        .linkContainer{
            background-color: rgb(231, 252, 156);
            border-radius: .3rem;
            padding: 1rem;
            min-height: 10rem;
            text-align: center;
        }
        .linkContainer:hover{
            box-shadow: 1rem 1rem 2rem rgb(134, 132, 132);
        }
        .linkDescription{
            width: fit-content;
            margin: 2rem auto;
        }
        a{
            font-size: 1.5rem;
            font-family: "Urbanist", sans-serif;
            display: block;
            padding: 1rem;
            color: black;
            background-color:rgba(217, 255, 0, 0.753);
            border-radius: .3rem;
            text-decoration: none;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-around;
            align-items: center;
        }
        a:hover{
            background-color: rgb(251, 255, 0);
        }
        a:visited,a:focus,a:active{
            text-decoration: none;
        }
        footer{
            padding: 1.5rem;
            min-height: 15vh;
            background-color: rgb(231, 252, 156);
            border-radius: 1.5rem 1.5rem 0rem 0rem;
        }
        @media (max-width:850px)
        {
            .allLinks{
                grid-template-columns: 45% 45%;
                gap: 2rem;
            }
        }
        @media (max-width:650px) 
        {
            .allLinks{
                grid-template-columns: auto;
            }    
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <header>
        <div class="heading">
            H-API
            <div class="sub">
                H-API is a RESTfull API server providing comprehensive information about me ( Munimadugu Sree Harsha). This collection of self-developed APIs offers detailed insights into various aspects of my professional and personal background.
            </div>
        </div>
    </header>
    <main>
        <div class="allLinks">
            <div class="linkContainer">
                 <a href="/user/achievements" > Achievements API 
                    <span class="material-symbols-outlined">
                        open_in_new
                    </span>
                 </a> 
                <div class="linkDescription">
                   Know my achievements
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="linkContainer">
                <a href="/user/badges" > Badges API 
                    <span class="material-symbols-outlined">
                        open_in_new
                    </span>
                </a> 
                <div class="linkDescription">
                    Check out my Badges
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="linkContainer">
                <a href="/user/certifications" > Certifications API 
                    <span class="material-symbols-outlined">
                        open_in_new
                    </span>
                </a> 
                <div class="linkDescription">
                    Here are some of the certificates I've earned.
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="linkContainer">
                <a href="/user/contacts" > Contact Info API 
                    <span class="material-symbols-outlined">
                        open_in_new
                    </span>
                </a> 
                <div class="linkDescription">
                    Ways to contact me ...
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="linkContainer">
                 <a href="/user/projects" > Projects API 
                    <span class="material-symbols-outlined">
                        open_in_new
                    </span>
                 </a> 
                <div class="linkDescription">
                    I invite you to explore my recent projects.
                </div>
                </div>

            <div class="linkContainer">
                 <a href="/user/skills" > Skills API 
                    <span class="material-symbols-outlined">
                        open_in_new
                    </span>
                 </a> 
                <div class="linkDescription">
                    I am particularly skilled at ...
                </div>
                </div>
        </div>
    </main>
    <footer>
        <div class="developer"> Developer : <b> M . Sree Harsha </b> </div>
        <div class="mail"> Contact me : <b><email>marvelavengersharsha@gmail.com</email></b> </div>
    </footer>
</body>
</html>